  <h id="temporal"><i>an(n)</i> as a temporal preposition</h>
  <p>With years – <ulx id="year">
      <lix>
        <gd>Rugadh am feallsanach Soren Kierkegaard <m>ann sa’ bhliadhna 1813</m>, an Copenhagen far
          na bhàsaich e nuair a bha e dà fhichead, ’s a dhà.</gd>
        <tr>The philosopher Soren Kierkegaard was born <u>in 1813</u>, in Copenhagen where he died
          when he was 42.</tr>
        <ref text="400-41">td. 103</ref>
      </lix>
    </ulx>
  </p>
  <p>With decades – <ulx id="decades">
      <lix>
        <gd>Ann an Dùn Èideann <m>anns na naochadan</m> bha barrachd agus barrachd inbhich airson
          Gàidhlig ionnsachadh.</gd>
        <tr>In Edinburgh <u>in the 90s</u> there were more and more people wanting to learn
          Gaelic.</tr>
        <ref text="610">td. 85</ref>
      </lix>
    </ulx>
  </p>
  <p>With time intervals – <ulx id="time-extent">
      <lix>
        <gd><m>Ann an dà bhliadhna dheug</m> sgrìobh e fichead leabhar ’s a h-aon ’s dh’ fhàg e
          grunn mór phàipearan a chùl air a sin.</gd>
        <tr><u>In 12 years</u> he [Kierkegaard] wrote 21 books and he left behind a large quantity
          of papers.</tr>
        <ref text="400-41">td. 103</ref>
      </lix>
    </ulx>
  </p>
